sentences.english: Unlike those of the West, Chinese loans are "no strings attached."
sentences.chinese: 不象西方国家，中国的贷款是“无附带条件”。

sentences.english: So watch out for these tests because they happen all the time。
sentences.chinese: 所以，要当心这些测试，因为它们无时不在。

sentences.english: With no wind indoors, for example, sweat will not evaporate as effectively.
sentences.chinese: 比如说室内无风，就不能有效蒸发汗水。

sentences.english: Other 5 monomers had no obvious effect on the expression of HIF-1.
sentences.chinese: 其它5种单体与对照比较无明显作用趋势。

sentences.english: There were insignificant effects on the fertility rate by cutting barley awn.
sentences.chinese: 剪芒对大麦结实率无显著影响。

sentences.english: Non -stress test has a higher clinical value in foretelling perinatal prognosis ofp olyhydramnios.
sentences.chinese: 无激惹试验在其预测围生儿预后具有较好的临床价值。

sentences.english: This study demonstrated A. pseudoalhagi extract has no significant side effects on rats.
sentences.chinese: 本研究证明骆驼刺提取物对大鼠无明显毒副作用。

sentences.english: Money can be good or bad, but prajna is always good.
sentences.chinese: 财富有善有恶，般若则无有不善。

sentences.english: However, there was no significant difference in the lowest SaO2 between the two groups.
sentences.chinese: 两组之间最低血氧饱和度的差异无显著性意义。

sentences.english: The values obtained with toroidal cores at room temperature unless otherwise shown.
sentences.chinese: 无说明，各项数值均系环型磁芯在室温下测得。

sentences.english: Sleeping at last in a dreamless sleep locked fast.
sentences.chinese: 终于在无梦的睡眠中睡得香。

sentences.english: This eye disease in menstrual quantity is little or no period of women.
sentences.chinese: 这种眼病多见于月经量少或无月经的女性。

sentences.english: A critic is a legless man who teaches running.
sentences.chinese: 批评家，是教人跑步的无腿的人。

sentences.english: They might be,for example,in an accident, and come close to being killed,but walk away without a scratch.
sentences.chinese: 比如说在事故中幸存，差点送命，但结果毫发无伤。

sentences.english: I can't go along with you on that, I'm afraid.
sentences.chinese: 恐怕在这一点上无不能认同你的说法。
